data.description: This aesthetically pleasing Victorian, located on a corner lot, features 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. Hardwood floors and natural woodwork highlighted throughout a majority of the home. Country-Style kitchen with an oversized island and appliances included! Large, covered porch that wraps around the front of the home. There is covered patio space just off the detached 2 car garage perfect for lounging or cookouts. Outside of the garage is equipped with hot tub hookups. Shop space on backside of garage with water available. Hot water tank installed in 2019. Come tour this charming move in ready home and fall in love with all its character! Forestville Central Schools.
